ITERATOR
--------

    April 01, 2012; <andrew.international@gmail.com>

Iterated Function System [1] [2] Explorer.

Run the program as follows, with the '-F' option to specify full-screen.

    $ ./bin/explorer.sh [-F]

[1] http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Iterated_function_system
[2] Construction of fractal objects with iterated function systems,
    Demko, Stephen and Hodges, Laurie and Naylor, Bruce,
    SIGGRAPH Computer Graphics, Volume 19, Number 3, 1985, 
    http://www-users.cs.umn.edu/~bstanton/pdf/p271-demko.pdf

